      "id": "4237ca16303a5e06",
      "text": "There is something we seemingly cannot escape doing when we tackle a problem. We typically take it for granted, but it is of the utmost importance. Pretty much the first thing we will do is to separate ourselves from the problem in order to observe it."
    },
